                    <h2>Server Rules</h2>
                    <br/>
                    <h6>Universal Rules</h6>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Respect all members of the server.</li>
                        <li>Harassment and repeated and/or repeated malicious words and actions towards members is prohibited.</li>
                        <li>Compliance with staff is required.</li>
                        <li>Discussions involving self-harm, torture, homicide, or other forms of malice are prohibited.</li>
                        <li>Hostility towards the server and its members using any medium of lingual exchange is prohibited.</li>
                        <li>Hostile actions towards the server and other incorporated infrastructures are prohibited.</li>
                        <li>Impersonation of other members, staff, and the owners is prohibited.</li>
                        <li>The use of excessive capitalization is prohibited.</li>
                        <li>Attempting to conduct transactions involving Minecraft accounts or offline assets is prohibited.</li>
                        <li>Overtly sexual, racial, religious, political, sexist, and otherwise vulgar and politically incorrect language, pictures, names, nicknames, and web links are prohibited (Read: noninclusivity).</li>
                        <li>Homonyms and innuendoes to bypass the previous rule are prohibited.</li>
                        <li>Discussions involving drugs or drug use of any kind (medical or otherwise) are prohibited.</li>
                        <li>Encouragement to violate the rules will be met with punishment equivalent to that corresponding to the rule(s) being encouraged to violate.</li>
                        <li>Disclosure of personal information, both one’s own and everyone else’s, is prohibited.</li>
                        <li>Mention of servers other than FadeCloud and their advertisement in any form is prohibited.</li>
                        <li>Punishment evasion in any form is prohibited.</li>
                    </ol>
                    
                    <h6>Server Rules</h6>

                    <i>General</i>

                    <ol>
                      <li>Noninclusive plots and signs are prohibited.</li>
                      <li>Mentions or advertisement of servers other than FadeCloud in any form is prohibited.</li>
                      <li>Hacked clients and mods that provide unfair competitive advantage are prohibited.</li>
                      <li>The use macros for idling activities or to provide competitive edge is prohibited.</li>
                      <li>Creating spam containing unintelligible characters and the repetition of messages spaced less than 60 seconds apart using any medium of lingual exchange is prohibited.</li>
                      <li>Bypassing the chat filter is prohibited.</li>
                      <li>Flying into or during combat is prohibited.</li>
                      <li>Combat from the boundary formed between the Safezone and the Warzone is prohibited.</li>
                      <li>The use of glitches of any kind to access otherwise unreachable areas or to provide competitive advantage is prohibited.</li>
                      <li>The use of commands to remove items from one’s inventory during combat is prohibited.</li>
                      <li>Malicious actions toward Safezones and Warzones are prohibited.</li>
                    </ol>
                    
                    <i>Prison</i>

                    <ol>
                      <li>Violating event rules is prohibited.</li>
                      <li>Malicious actions toward members’ plots are prohibited.</li>
                    </ol>
                    
                    <b><i><center>These rules are subject to change at any time with or without notice, please check back frequently for updates.</b></i></center>
